### Add to Cart - Success Case
POST http://localhost:5000/api/cart/items
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "variantId": "{{variantId}}",
  "quantity": 2
}

###

### Add to Cart - Increment Existing Item
POST http://localhost:5000/api/cart/items
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "variantId": "{{variantId}}",
  "quantity": 1
}

###

### Add to Cart - Missing Variant ID
POST http://localhost:5000/api/cart/items
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 2
}

###

### Add to Cart - Invalid Quantity (Zero)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/cart/items
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "variantId": "{{variantId}}",
  "quantity": 0
}

###

### Add to Cart - Invalid Quantity (Negative)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/cart/items
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "variantId": "{{variantId}}",
  "quantity": -5
}

###

### Add to Cart - Exceeds Max Quantity
POST http://localhost:5000/api/cart/items
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "variantId": "{{variantId}}",
  "quantity": 15
}

###

### Add to Cart - Non-existent Variant
POST http://localhost:5000/api/cart/items
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "variantId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "quantity": 1
}

###

### Add to Cart - Without Auth
POST http://localhost:5000/api/cart/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "variantId": "{{variantId}}",
  "quantity": 2
}

###
